cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this portal or the unified scRNA-seq metadata catalog in
  your research, please cite it as below. A formal publication is
  planned; until then please cite the software repository directly.
title: "SCeQTL Portal (SGDB) — A unified search and discovery portal for single-cell RNA-seq metadata"
type: software
version: "3.0.0"
date-released: "2026-05-15"
license: MIT
url: "https://github.com/firefly-hefeng/SGDB_Agent"
repository-code: "https://github.com/firefly-hefeng/SGDB_Agent"
abstract: >-
  SCeQTL Portal unifies 943,732 human single-cell RNA-seq samples from
  8 curated sources (GEO, EGA, NCBI, EBI, CellxGene, PsychAD, HTAN, HCA)
  into a single ontology-aligned catalog. The portal pairs an offline
  curated search with a live cross-database discovery agent that fans a
  single natural-language query out to 6 federated databases — GEO, SRA,
  EBI BioStudies, Single-Cell Expression Atlas (SCEA), CellxGene, HCA —
  in parallel, deduplicates the results, and returns them as SSE.
keywords:
  - single-cell RNA-seq
  - metadata
  - ontology
  - faceted search
  - scientific data portal
  - cross-database discovery
authors:
  # Author list will be finalised when a peer-reviewed publication is
  # prepared. The repo owner is the current maintainer.
  - given-names: "hefeng"
    family-names: "(firefly-hefeng)"
